      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "There is big furry in real es\ntate west of Hangman creek, close\nto the right of way of the North\nCoast railway. Certain pieces of\nreal estate in that region have\nbeen advanced from 80 to 100 per\ncent in the last four or five weeks,\nand no one is ready to say why\nii is\n\n\nThe reason for the advance is\nfound in numerous purchases in\nthat region made by Baldwin &\nPfile, presumably for the North\nCoast. 1t is reported that the\nNorth Coast will either locate its\nshops there or is preparing for\nmuch larger switching capacity\nthan at first planned and that this\nreal estate is being bought for this\npurpose. Anyway, it has sent the\nprices of property in the West\nGrove region soaring."
    }
